---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About Author - Fragrant Signatures"
  description="Learn more about Slobodanka Poštić, author of Fragrant Signatures and ambassador for Croatia at Airmid Institute."
  currentPath="/en/about-author/"
  lang="en"
>
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-botanical-50 via-white to-nature-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 max-w-6xl">
      <!-- Hero Section -->
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <!-- Logo -->
        <div class="mb-8">
          <img 
            src="/images/fw-logo-red.png" 
            alt="Fragrant Signatures Logo" 
            class="max-w-md h-auto mx-auto"
          />
        </div>
        
        <!-- Stylized Divider -->
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-8">
          <div class="flex-1 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-botanical-300 to-transparent"></div>
          <div class="mx-4 w-3 h-3 bg-gradient-to-br from-botanical-400 to-nature-400 rounded-full"></div>
          <div class="flex-1 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-botanical-300 to-transparent"></div>
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="text-5xl text-botanical-800 mb-6">
          About Author
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-botanical-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
         
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Author Content -->
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start mb-16">
        <!-- Author Image -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="relative rounded-3xl shadow-2xl overflow-hidden">
            <img 
              src="/images/Slobodanka_Postic.jpg" 
              alt="Slobodanka Poštić - author of Fragrant Signatures"
              class="w-full h-auto object-cover"
            />
          </div>
          
        </div>

        <!-- Author Bio -->
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <h2 class="text-3xl text-botanical-800">Slobodanka Poštić</h2>
          
          <div class="bg-botanical-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-botanical-200">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-normal text-botanical-800 mb-3">Educational Activity</h3>
            <p class="text-botanical-700 leading-relaxed">
              Since 2005, she has been dedicated to natural perfumery, through designing and holding various workshops and courses, as well as establishing Fragrant Signatures the School of Natural Perfumery.
            </p>
            <p class="text-botanical-700 leading-relaxed mt-4">
              Slobodanka also manages a resourceful website about aromatherapy, natural perfumery and olfactory experiences: <a href="https://www.aromaterapija.info" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-botanical-600 hover:text-botanical-800 underline font-medium transition-colors duration-300">www.aromaterapija.info</a>
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-nature-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-nature-200">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-normal text-nature-800 mb-3">Airmid Institute Ambassador</h3>
            <p class="text-nature-700 leading-relaxed">
              Since 2021, she has been involved in the work of the <a href="https://airmidinstitute.org/airmid-global-ambassadors/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-nature-600 hover:text-nature-800 underline font-medium transition-colors duration-300">Airmid Institute</a> for the Protection of Medicinal and Aromatic Plants as their ambassador to Croatia.
            </p>
          </div>
          
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Main Content -->
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
        <!-- About the writing process -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-2 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/90 to-botanical-50/30 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 pr-4 lg:pr-8 shadow-xl border border-botanical-200 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="text-center mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl text-botanical-800 mb-3">About the writing process</h2>
            <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-botanical-400 to-nature-400 mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
          </div>
        
          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-ink-800 leading-relaxed space-y-6">
            <p>
              Slobodanka Poštić, nature admirer and teacher, is the author of several books on aromatherapy.
            </p>
            
            <p>
              Since 2005, she has been dedicated to natural perfumery, through designing and holding various workshops and courses, as well as establishing Fragrant Signatures the School of Natural Perfumery.
            </p>
            
            <p>
              Since 2021, she has been involved in the work of the Airmid Institute for the Protection of Medicinal and Aromatic Plants as their ambassador to Croatia.
            </p>
            
            <p>
              Slobodanka also manages a resourceful website about aromatherapy, natural perfumery and olfactory experiences: <a href="https://www.aromaterapija.info" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-botanical-600 hover:text-botanical-800 underline font-medium transition-colors duration-300">www.aromaterapija.info</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Contact Card -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-50 to-botanical-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-accent-200 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 h-fit">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-500 to-botanical-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 4.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-normal text-accent-800">Contact</h3>
              <p class="text-accent-600 text-sm">Get in touch with the author</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a 
            href="mailto:slo.postic@gmail.com" 
            class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-500 to-botanical-500 text-white rounded-lg hover:from-accent-600 hover:to-botanical-600 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 text-sm font-medium"
          >
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 4.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
            Send Email
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Navigation -->
      <div class="mt-8 flex justify-center">
        <a 
          href="/en/about-manual/" 
          class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-nature-600 to-nature-700 text-white rounded-xl hover:from-nature-700 hover:to-nature-800 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl font-medium"
        >
          ← About Manual
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
